attributes.title: Lazer Team Behind the Scenes - Episode 2
attributes.caption: Episode 2
attributes.description: We're back to entice you with another look into the behind-the-scenes of Lazer Team! This month, the crew finishes up pre-production and begins shooting the movie! Will we spoil everything for you in this video You'll just have to keep watching to find out (Spoilers: probably not. We love you too much to spoil it for you).
attributes.display_title: Lazer Team Behind the Scenes - Episode 2

attributes.title: Lazer Team Behind the Scenes - Episode 3
attributes.caption: Lazer Team may have wrapped production, but that doesn't mean we can't pretend to all be on set right now! This month, we give you a behind-the-scenes look at life on the set Lazer Team. Explosions! Goofing off! Cameras! Lights! Relatively creepy mustaches! You can see all these things and more in this month's Lazer Team BTS video.

attributes.title: Lazer Team Behind the Scenes - Episode 5
attributes.caption: ​Lazer Team is ready to make it's public debut in theaters on January 27, 2016! But until then, take a look at this episode where we are given an in-depth look at the Special Effects team and what really goes into making the movie look amazing.
attributes.description: Lazer Team is ready to make its theatrical debut on January 27, 2016! While you wait, take a look at this episode where we are given an in-depth look at the Special Effects team and what really goes into making the movie look amazing. Check out Matt's bad Texan accent in this month's Lazer Team BTS video.

attributes.title: Lazer Team Behind the Scenes – Episode 6
attributes.caption: With our finale episode of Lazer Team's Behind-the-Scenes here, it's time to delve into what made the sounds of the movie come alive. Meet Jeff Williams and Video Game Orchestra, headed by Shota Nakama, as they work together to craft the soundtrack.

Meet Jeff Williams and Video Game Orchestra, headed by Shota Nakama, as they work together to craft the soundtrack that is now available on iTunes!
